data.description: Veterans! Take advantage of Seller's VA assumable loan at 4.375% interest rate! This large 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home on 1.5 acres is nestled in the heart of the desirable community of Moyie Springs. Recently updated with all new interior paint, new laminate flooring and gourmet kitchen, this home has something for everyone. Master ensuite has a jack and jill bthrm with double shower heads and separate large jetted tub, 3 more comfortable bedrooms, breakfast nook off the kitchen and an extra space for a formal dining rm or family rm/den. Kitchen has been outfitted with all new appliances including an impressive 6 burner gas stove. Vaulted ceilings and large picture windows add character and charm to this inviting home. Have peace of mind with the log burning woodstove for an excellent backup heat option or main heat source to lower your utility bill. A new double carport was added last year along with a freshly graveled driveway. There is plenty of room to spread out on this expansive property from the large fenced in backyard, to the sprawling front lawn, garden areas and the privacy of the surrounding mature evergreens.
